org.jppf.client

Class JPPFResultCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jppf.client.JPPFResultCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, TaskResultListener, SubmissionStatusHandler

    public class JPPFResultCollector
extends Object
implements TaskResultListener, SubmissionStatusHandler
    Implementation of the TaskResultListener interface that can be used "as is" to collect the results of an asynchronous job submission.
    See Also:
    JPPFClient.submit(org.jppf.client.JPPFJob)
